    <label>A803N Motion Sensor</label>
    <description><![CDATA[
Motion Sensor<br /><h1>Overview</h1><p>Motion sensor (PIR) is a passive infrared detector or physical sensor.</p> <br /><h2>Inclusion Information</h2><p>Press the PIR button 3 times</p> <br /><h2>Exclusion Information</h2><p>Press the PIR button 3 times</p> <br /><h2>Wakeup Information</h2><p>Press the PIR Button</p>
    ]]></description>
